{"type": "article", "id": 6755, "title": "烹饪桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-25T07:18:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052342421WwqVHhkSEAIzLUj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款烹饪桌是德国设计师 Moritz Putizer 的毕业设计作品。在设计过程中，Moritz Putizer 并没有将焦点放在食物本身，而是致力于将整个烹饪的过程中有可能带来的创造性与信息交流的需求表达出来，烹饪不再是简单的做饭，而是看作一种社交活动的厨房环境。整个烹饪桌由两部分构成，配有一个可移动的燃气炉，它可以通过烹饪桌底部的隐藏滑轨插入，适应个性化的烹饪需求。气体炉外侧用圆形陶瓷碗包裹，起到衬垫和隔热的双重作用。值得一提的是，这款亮相今年科隆国际家具展上的作品还获得了 Pure Talent Contest 竞赛的一等奖。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234239aBqrQJipnOW9h2zZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342390y4PDCjIKiY59VBk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234240BzvK2jd6FwCN94qo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234240wm2hijHOCKeg4QR7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234241fIlj2407cXUQs3zA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523424172ErZl0khgGBANfK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76894866\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}